{"tid":455471,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【國歌法】唔畀二創 馬恩國引述李飛：馬場內奏歌觀眾要站立","createTime":"2017-11-02T06:17:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-02T11:42:31.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"4e3cc62dcc76401b16c5d2007318c67928f98ee5","tid":455471,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T06:17:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171102/large/1509602410_1415.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171102%2Flarge%2F1509602410_1415.jpg&h=0c254b2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中澳法學交流基金會訪京團今早與基本法委員會主任李飛會面，會後團長馬恩國引述李飛「講話」，指《國歌法》列入《基本法》附件三後，香港應按照本地實際情況立法，但立法時必須保留法例的核心要素，包括奏唱國歌時要有一定禮儀，例如未來在馬場奏國歌時，場內的馬迷亦要站立；亦要有強制性的中小學國歌教育，但並非要背誦歌詞，而是要令他們明白歌詞有中華民族抗日精神的背景。<br />\n<br />\n馬恩國又指，李飛所說的5項不能缺少的核心要素，包括曲譜要按《國歌法》附件訂明的標準、不可作商業用途、不可「二次創作」、改音改詞都不可、奏唱時要有禮儀並肅立。至於在公開場合污辱國歌的行為，例如在球場噓國歌，必須有規定去處理。<br />\n<br />\n馬恩國指李飛無提及追溯期，但有指出如香港沒有行政處分，就應處理如何以刑事處罰代替內地法例中的行政拘留。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171102/57407725\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171102%2F57407725&d=2qj4hJ%2F0yb%2FUxPeMlBt47HIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=78855d26\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171102%2F57407725&h=5b306179\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171102/57407725</a>"},{"pid":"68d101883c566117c9c28512ceab9189b3529464","tid":455471,"uid":61280,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T06:19:48.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">支狗蟈歌關你袋鼠漢奸鳩事咩！！！！</span></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"598a90bc5bdd8c603d38900549ebb81d91eef660","tid":455471,"uid":53687,"like":9,"dislike":0,"sc